{"tid":2322971,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)Cyberpunk2077","createTime":"2020-12-12T18:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T14:45:59.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2ab02242dca4ef67e587cdb4d053d20e97c28b65","tid":2322971,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T18:52:18.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">玩唔完下次玩返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcsF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=28b33526\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcsF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=be8c78bf\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcsF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=d3b76322\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/52/e2/14/52e2142e59eade27a8652714c033496c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F52%2Fe2%2F14%2F52e2142e59eade27a8652714c033496c.jpg&h=eeccb5df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《電馭叛客2077》是一款角色扮演遊戲。玩家扮演稱為「V」的可客製化角色。遊戲設定在加利福尼亞州的開放世界大都會夜城（Night City）。本作具有非英語角色，不懂該語言的玩家可以購買翻譯植入物以加深對他們的理解。不同植入物的翻譯品質會有所不同，更昂貴的植入物可以提供更準確的翻譯。「幻智之舞」（Braindance）是一種直接流入大腦的數字記錄裝置，可讓玩家體驗其他人的情緒、大腦活動和肌肉動作，如同自身。遊戲根據玩家的選擇會有不同的結局<br />\n<br />\n 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcsF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=cd62782a\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcsF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=7b5b0297\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02c2273ceb0947838c6721503f4c8cf167fe699","tid":2322971,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T19:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbd7b70ca067a543d5b75b365eefcc68848658b","tid":2322971,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T17:58:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/thanksyour\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fthanksyour&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcsF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=965ae7c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/thanksyour</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmo